&gt;&gt; How long does it
take, say it again.

00:21:37.290 --> 00:21:40.500
&gt;&gt; How long does it
take you to decide what

00:21:40.500 --> 00:21:42.230
to incorporate into [inaudible]?

00:21:42.230 --> 00:21:46.090
&gt;&gt; How long does it take what
to incorporate in the drawings?

00:21:46.090 --> 00:21:48.640
I'm actually pretty quick.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:52.400 position:56%
I can read a manuscript and have
all the sketches done in a few days.

00:21:52.400 --> 00:21:54.670
You know I just read it over
and over and over again.

